        <text>&lt;p&gt;{!Lapsed_Membership_Notifications.Account.Name},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This email is notify you that your membership with the National Diaper Bank Network and Alliance for Period Supplies, has lapsed as of &lt;strong&gt;December 31st, {!for_LastYear}&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If you would like to rejoin APS and/or the National Diaper Bank Network, please email programs@diaperbanknetwork.org.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We encourage you to renew your membership to continue taking advantage of the member exclusive benefits offered.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
