        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;Dear {!Renewal_Upcoming_Expiration_Notifications.Name},&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;On behalf of both the Alliance for Period Supplies and the National Diaper Bank Network, your membership is important and very much appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We know how busy you are running your program, so we wanted to take this opportunity to remind you that your membership will expire on &lt;strong&gt;December 31st, {!for_ThisYear}&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Please submit your membership dues at your earliest convenience in order to remain part of our community. It couldn&apos;t be easier - &lt;strong&gt;just click the link in the invoice you receive via email today.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your financial contributions truly are vital to creating more robust programs and resources, and so is your membership. Your membership creates the strong, vibrant community that the Network has become.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We look forward to working with you in the year to come.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;National Diaper Bank Network&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
